A collection of free fonts. 

Checkout the submodules:
    git submodule init
    git submodule update

On ubuntu, copy the new font folder to system font folder:
   cp -R programmer_fonts/droid-fonts/ ~/.fonts/truetype/ (user)
   sudo cp -R programmer_fonts/droid-fonts/ /usr/share/fonts/truetype/ (system)
   sudo fc-cache -f -v

On OSX:
   ~/Library/Fonts/ (user) 
   /Library/Fonts/ (system) 
